SUMMARY:Exhibit Reception | The Whimsical Naturalist by Katie Crawford
DESCRIPTION:Meet the artist and enjoy light refreshments at the exhibit reception for The Whimsical Naturalist on Sunday\, March 8 from 1-3 p.m.! \nIn this exhibit of original watercolors\, North Carolina artist Katie Crawford celebrates the rich biodiversity of the East Coast\, telling the story of interconnectedness between species\, ecosystems\, and communities. Through portraits of native plants and animals\, she uses anthropomorphism to shift perspectives and inspire visitors to consider how we are connected to our environment and each other. \nThe reception takes place in and around the gallery and is open to all. \nReminder: Sunday\, March 8 is the first day of Daylight Savings Time!
URL:https://ncbg.unc.edu/event/exhibit-reception-the-whimsical-naturalist/
LOCATION:North Carolina Botanical Garden\, 100 Old Mason Farm Road\, Chapel Hill\, NC\, 27517\, United States
CATEGORIES:Exhibits
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncbg.unc.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/963/2026/01/2026-01-09-Katie-Crawford-Exhibit-03-scaled.jpg
GEO:35.901081;-79.031939
